Services











SalesThe best tools streamline your practice, give a competitive advantage
          and increase the quality of service you provide to clients.





Broad and Unique Carrier Selection
Choice matters for you and your clients. Our carrier-agnostic approach
                  gives you a leg up on the competition.
View our products and carriers >





Proprietarty Strategy Tools
We provide needs-analysis and recommendation reports for delivery to your clients. These tools help educate the client and move them to action.





Underwriting Resources & Carrier Leverage
Put the best possible offer in front of your client.






Regular Lunch & Learns, Virtual Training, and our Altitude Retreat
Enjoy the perks of affiliation while exchanging effective sales and
                    marketing ideas.
Learn more about our incentives >













MarketingOur living is made when we are in front of clients. Allegis supports a
      broad range of programs to help promote your practice and increase
      business.




Seminar Marketing
Allegis offers various tried and true, turnkey seminar-marketing programs.
                Programs include all you need to succeed including invitations,
                presentations, and training. Some of our seasoned agents even deliver a
                few seminars for you to model the way and get you started.





Allegis Partners
For over 10 years, we have been helping agents develop income-
                producing relationships with CPA’s, attorneys, and P&C firms. Our turnkey
                program gets results and our in-house CPA helps you net and land these relationships.





Private Reserve Strategy and Circle of Wealth System
These proven programs deliver the tools you need to launch and sustain a
                successful career. Change how your clients look at their money and
                change your career.





Athletic Introductions
Break the ice with prospective clients and referral partners! This
                  proprietary Allegis program offers you a fun and creative way to connect
                  with clients and prospective clients through College and other athletic
                  events and contests.





Referral Marketing
Ask any successful business owner and you will find that referrals are the
                  life-blood of their business. Allegis will train you how to develop referral
                  networks and increase your ability to gather high-quality referrals. Without
                  exception, referrals are the best and lowest-cost way to build your client
                  base.





Policy and Beneficiary Audits
These turnkey programs give you all you need to successfully perform
                policy and/or beneficiary audits. These services are a huge value to
                consumers and help you get in front of more people.





Veteran Benefits Program
This marketing program gives you the tools to help veterans gain access
                to valuable government benefits of up to $23,388 per year. Contact your marketing consultant for more information.



















Back Office SupportLet us be your back office! Allegis has built a world-class back office
      that is easy to do business with.




Seasoned Underwriting Services & Tools
We have the ability to get you the best possible offer on all your cases and
      to help you place those challenging hard-to- place cases. Our Chief
      Underwriter has over 25 years of underwriting experience and will help
      you position the case, work with carrier underwriters, get the best offer
      and get your case placed.





State-of-the-Art Website and Technology
Paperless office, VoIP call center technology, electronic applications and
      more! Access our website anytime to track your Allegis Points, run quotes,
      access forms, and much more.





Easy Paperwork Submission
Submit via our app, fax, email or mail.





A Seasoned Team of Professionals
Each with several years of experience in doing what they do!





App-Assist Programs with Several Carriers
Submit a simplified one-page app, and we do the rest!





Electronic Contracting
One and done! Take 10 minutes to fill out our contracting kit and you can
      be licensed with any or ALL of the carriers we represent.




         
      





Reach out to us
We'd love to tell you more about what we do and how we can help your independent practice.
Call 800-418-1788
Email Us


















