                Welcome
              









About
Allegis Wealth Advisors was founded with the goal of assisting our clients in every aspect of their financial lives. We’ve provided the most personal service available, thus earning a reputation for excellence in our industry. For each of our clients we strive to help create financial stability and security to provide financial independence.



Company
Our mission is to assist you in building financial strength and protection for you, your family, and your business. We employ the most talented, professional, and knowledgeable people in the industry to support you in those efforts.
Find Out More









Our Locations






South Jordan, UT




Provo, UT




Farmington, UT




Idaho Falls, ID








Services
At Allegis Wealth Advisors, we have a vast knowledge in the financial space and provide assistance to those in need. Check out all that we have to offer.
