Learn More
As a full-service insurance and investment company, Allegis Financial Partners focuses on the individual needs of each client – not a particular product. This has proven to be a winning formula for our company, founded in 1999 by Jeff Erekson, and consistently recognized as one of the Intermountain West’s strongest and most stable agencies. During the last 10 years, our sales increased nearly five-fold as we expanded to six locations with more than 100 associates in Idaho, Utah, Washington and Oregon.

